🏗️ System Architecture & Tooling
Frontend Experience: Framer — used to build a high-conversion, guided entry point for customers.

Data Collection: Google Forms — provides a structured schema for capturing order details consistently.

Transaction Processing: Paystack — handles the secure financial layer and provides the API hooks for validation.

Logic & Integration: n8n.io — the "System Glue" that listens for payments and updates the database automatically.

Primary Database: Airtable — acts as the "Single Source of Truth," linking customers, payments, and orders.

Business Intelligence: Looker Studio — visualizes the database into real-time charts for executive decision-making.



🚀 Why this Stack?
Modular: You can upgrade any piece (e.g., moving from Sheets to a SQL database) without rebuilding the entire system.

Low Friction: Customers don't need to create accounts; the system tracks them via unique identifiers (Phone/Email).

Cost-Effective: Uses high-performance tools that scale with the business volume.
